         <div type="edition" ana="#b1" xml:lang="heb" subtype="transcription" xml:id="beth0237.transcription" corresp="#beth0237.translation">
            <p>כן הן מנחות אטיו בתו של רבי<lb/> גמליאל בן נחמיה שמתה<lb/> בתולה בת עשרין ושתים<lb/>
               שנה ואטיון בתו של רבי<lb/> יהודה בנו של רבי גמליאל<lb/> שמתה בת תשע<lb/> שנים<lb/>
               וששה חודשים עמידת<supplied reason="lost">ן</supplied>
               <supplied reason="lost">עם</supplied>
               <supplied reason="lost">הצדיקים</supplied>
            </p>
         </div>
         <div type="translation" ana="#b1" xml:id="beth0237.translation" corresp="#beth0237.transcription">
            <p>Here they lie, <name type="gpatr">
                  <persName xml:lang="la " ref="persons.xml#beth0237p01">Atio</persName>, the <rs type="family" ana="interpretations.xml#daughter">daughter </rs> of <rs type="religTitle" ana="interpretations.xml#rabbi">Rabbi </rs>
                  <persName type="patr" xml:lang="hbo " ref="persons.xml#beth0237p02">Gamaliel</persName>, <rs type="family" ana="interpretations.xml#son">son </rs> of <persName type="gpatr" xml:lang="hbo " ref="persons.xml#beth0237p03">Nehemiah </persName>
               </name>, who died a <rs type="epithet" ana="interpretations.xml#virgin">virgin </rs> at the age of <num type="age">twenty-two</num> years, and <name type="gpatr">
                  <persName xml:lang="la " ref="persons.xml#beth0237p04">Ation</persName>, the <rs type="family" ana="interpretations.xml#daughter">daughter </rs> of
                            <rs type="religTitle" ana="interpretations.xml#rabbi">Rabbi </rs>
                  <persName type="patr" xml:lang="hbo " ref="persons.xml#beth0237p05">Judah </persName>
                  <rs type="family" ana="interpretations.xml#son">son </rs> of <rs type="religTitle" ana="interpretations.xml#rabbi">Rabbi </rs>
                  <persName type="gpatr" xml:lang="hbo " ref="persons.xml#beth0237p06">Gamaliel </persName>
               </name>, who died at the age of <num type="age">nine</num> years and <num type="age">six</num> months. <rs type="formula" ana="interpretations.xml#resurrection">May their resurrection [be with the
                righteous]</rs>.</p>
         </div>
